# Project Guidelines

- Maintain changelog entries in CHANGELOG.md

## Code Style & Patterns

- Prefer composition over inheritance
- Use repository pattern for data access
- For modules in utils/ and lib/, use functional programming practices

## Testing Standards

- Unit tests required for business logic, especially for all modules in utils/ and lib/

## Project Context

- This is a next.js-based application. Use convention next.js practices
- This is a personal blog web site built with next.js, with contents in public/contents/ in the form of markdown
- This project use node and npm
- Respect eslint and prettier
- For tests, respect jest convention practices
- Use fish shell
